BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Great American Trailer Park Musical
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260722T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260722T220000
DTSTAMP:20260713T161540Z
UID:occ-1408@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Musical Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Nehls and Kelso's trashy\, big-hearted comedy of adultery\, ag
 oraphobia\, and hurricanes at a Florida trailer park.\n\nDavid Nehls and B
 etsy Kelso's musical comedy\, an Off-Broadway hit in 2005\, set at Armadil
 lo Acres trailer park in Starke\, Florida. Jeannie hasn't stepped outside 
 her trailer in twenty years\; her tollbooth-collector husband Norbert is l
 osing patience\; and Pippi\, a stripper hiding out from a marker-huffing e
 x with a gun named Bertha\, has just moved in next door. The affair that f
 ollows kicks up a storm in more ways than one. From New Depot Players\, th
 e Conyers community theatre.
GEO:33.6671075;-84.0180229
LAST-MODIFIED:20260713T161459Z
LOCATION:Conyers Rockdale Council for the Arts\, 910 Center St NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.tix.com/ticket-sales/thenewdepotplayers/5082/event/1473887
END:VEVENT
